OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with showers or
OL,7,Flonger spells of rain moving
OL,8,Fnortheast, possibly heavy at times.
OL,9,FThen becoming drier later in the
OL,10,Fevening with a few cloud breaks. Light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FDry in the morning with
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Thickening cloud and
OL,15,Foutbreaks of light rain will spread
OL,16,Fnorth into Orkney in the afternoon,
OL,17,Fthen into Shetland in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
