OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOvernight
OL,6,Frain clearing away in the morning then
OL,7,Fdry with some hazy sunshine, haar at
OL,8,Ffirst across Shetland, a few showers
OL,9,Fpossible in the evening. Mainly dry
OL,10,Fover the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
